reviews.review_text:
Disrespected? you have lost your tolerance for being "disrespected"?
well if you would post decent quality sounding recordings, maybe you wouldn't be "disrespected"
there is obviously something wrong with the speed of the recording on this show. sounds horrible.
if all your uploads sound this bad, disrespect is in order. i would rate this quality a corner of one star if i could, a full one star is too nice.
as an "old taper", you should know quality from shit, and this is shit.
